XfrpRawTokenKind {...}{.pure.} = enum
  Ignore, Comment, Comma, LBracket, RBracket, LParen, RParen, Colon, At, Slash,
  Equal, Module, Material, In, Out, Use, Node, Init, True, False, If, Then,
  Else, Last, Function, InfixLeft, InfixRight, InfixNone, Magic, Emit, Id,
  Operator, FDigits, Digits, TripleQuoted, Unknown
